# Prisma
# Note: we now track prisma/migrations/ in git.
# The culinary schema historically used `prisma db push` (no migration files),
# but the commerce schema (schema.commerce.prisma) uses the standard
# `prisma migrate` workflow because real payment data needs a replayable
# migration history. Commerce migrations live in backend/prisma/migrations/.

